1. *Sad* se već zahuktavao vetar. (Now the wind was already picking up.) 
2. *Sad* je već sve bilo gotovo. (Now everything was already done.)
3. Ona se *sad* oseća mnogo bolje. (She now feels much better.)
4. *Sad* je vreme da se odmorimo. (It is time to rest now.)
5. *Sad* će svi biti zadovoljni. (Now everyone will be satisfied.)